    "description": "Reliance Digital Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a SEO Specialist for our Kolkata operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Reliance Digital Ventures Solutions:\nReliance Digital Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Digital Ventures Solutions!",
